        "Undoubtedly it is true fact that in the cutting-edge era technology is developing day by day . Few parties say that computers have made soul smoothly and more comfortable . While others believe that computers have made life more difficult and stressful . This essay will discuss both  views. And I will discuss my opinion in further paragraphs .",
        "To commence with , the computer is essential for every masses life . It helps to complete such type of job like  employment , education  regarding personal production. To explain it , in the modern epoch without computers human being can not complete their performance . So to complete this trial technology must be essential . For instance ,in every sector computer is always used and it makes easier and luxury growth ,Moreover it reduces the expenses of production and helps with term management . Hence , the computer makes a part of the human soul .",
        "On another hand, by changing occasions stress levels increased among the masses with the help of computers. To illustrate , by developing the computer illegal production done by women increases stress and complexity among  folks . For example, harassment and other illegal production were done at a very high level with the help of computers and sometimes stage entity lost their thinking . Although , it reduces our eyesight level . Thus , the computer makes individuals' life very complex and stressful .",
